  <ul class="privacyul">
    <li>Your name</li>
    <li>Email address</li>
    <li>Phone number</li>
    <li>Account data such as your profile and courses</li>
    <li>Data related to content shared by you</li>
    <li>Data about your account on other services</li>
    <li>Data through promotions and surveys</li>
    <li>Data regarding any support concerns</li>
    <li>Information about your device</li>
    <li>Parts of our services you use</li>
